1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,950
=Episode 18=

23
00:01:55,271 --> 00:01:55,712
Hello?

24
00:02:09,312 --> 00:02:10,232
What's going on?

25
00:02:11,151 --> 00:02:11,990
I confirmed it again.

26
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,151
The palm oil order
we planned to import from Indonesia

27
00:02:14,151 --> 00:02:15,151
was intercepted.

28
00:02:15,431 --> 00:02:16,050
Who took it?

29
00:02:16,232 --> 00:02:16,990
We can't find out.

30
00:02:17,831 --> 00:02:20,110
The Indonesian side
refunded the deposit,

31
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,831
but they refused to say
who took the order.

32
00:02:21,831 --> 00:02:23,912
Can't we switch to another supplier?

33
00:02:23,912 --> 00:02:24,792
It's not that simple.

34
00:02:25,151 --> 00:02:26,752
Jinxin Food has strict standards.

35
00:02:26,792 --> 00:02:30,472
The palm oil we use must have
an acid value between 0.8 and 1.2.

36
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:33,690
The only plantation that meets the standard
and can guarantee the supply volume

37
00:02:33,831 --> 00:02:34,991
is the company in Indonesia.

38
00:02:35,632 --> 00:02:37,632
Food safety is our bottom line.

39
00:02:38,192 --> 00:02:39,792
If we lower our standards

40
00:02:39,952 --> 00:02:41,551
because of supply issues,

41
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,690
I'd rather halt production.

42
00:02:47,512 --> 00:02:48,512
Mr. Qin is right.

43
00:02:49,312 --> 00:02:51,111
Food safety is the bottom line.

44
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:52,999
We can change ingredients,

45
00:02:53,391 --> 00:02:54,962
but we can never lower standards.

46
00:02:55,472 --> 00:02:55,991
Li,

47
00:02:56,431 --> 00:02:58,991
check again who intercepted that order.

48
00:02:59,192 --> 00:03:00,192
If we can find out,

49
00:03:00,352 --> 00:03:01,831
we'll try to buy it back from them.

50
00:03:02,025 --> 00:03:02,826
Okay.

51
00:03:06,632 --> 00:03:08,111
But this happened so suddenly.

52
00:03:08,192 --> 00:03:10,431
This interception must've been planned.

53
00:03:10,450 --> 00:03:13,390
If we try to buy it back, they might name
a price so high it bankrupts us.

54
00:03:17,192 --> 00:03:17,752
Shanshan,

55
00:03:18,232 --> 00:03:18,991
what do you think?

56
00:03:19,111 --> 00:03:20,271
I...

57
00:03:20,271 --> 00:03:21,790
We don't have time
to think it through right now.

58
00:03:22,192 --> 00:03:22,792
Qin Jiamin,

59
00:03:23,032 --> 00:03:25,551
take more people tomorrow
to contact plantations

60
00:03:25,551 --> 00:03:26,752
and inspect palm oil.

61
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:29,090
I'll prepare a contingency plan
in case we have to suspend production.

62
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,551
Why did you interrupt Shanshan just now?

63
00:03:40,151 --> 00:03:42,192
Aren't you trying to groom her
to take over Jinxin?

64
00:03:42,632 --> 00:03:44,431
Then why not let her
be involved in this?

65
00:03:45,752 --> 00:03:47,660
I'm not someone
who never learns from mistakes.

66
00:03:48,032 --> 00:03:49,075
Besides, she said

67
00:03:49,525 --> 00:03:51,444
she doesn't want to live
by my expectations.

68
00:03:52,712 --> 00:03:54,552
I can't keep forcing her.

69
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:58,190
I'll handle these messy problems.

70
00:03:58,632 --> 00:04:01,312
As long as she can pursue her dream
without worries,

71
00:04:01,431 --> 00:04:02,375
I'll be satisfied.

72
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:05,391
You handle things with flexibility.

73
00:04:06,352 --> 00:04:07,391
You're not bad yourself.

74
00:04:09,431 --> 00:04:10,232
By the way,

75
00:04:11,551 --> 00:04:12,991
don't say I didn't warn you.

76
00:04:13,752 --> 00:04:14,990
Jiamin might be a bit suspicious

77
00:04:15,792 --> 00:04:17,512
about what happened today.

78
00:04:18,552 --> 00:04:19,791
I know what you mean.

79
00:04:20,552 --> 00:04:21,312
I suspect

80
00:04:21,831 --> 00:04:24,391
this batch of palm oil
is in Zhou Zeyang's hands.

81
00:04:27,231 --> 00:04:30,552
But his company is small.

82
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:33,310
Where would he get the capital
to buy all the palm oil?

83
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:35,900
- Zhang Guolong.
- Zhang Guolong.

84
00:04:38,711 --> 00:04:40,831
If they're really working together,

85
00:04:40,850 --> 00:04:41,962
there must be a backup plan.

86
00:04:42,831 --> 00:04:43,632
Here's what we do.

87
00:04:44,552 --> 00:04:46,231
To keep things under control,

88
00:04:46,391 --> 00:04:48,512
you need to make a public statement

89
00:04:48,512 --> 00:04:49,791
as the chairman of Jinxin,

90
00:04:49,831 --> 00:04:51,432
reassure employees and shareholders,

91
00:04:51,752 --> 00:04:52,952
and promise everyone

92
00:04:52,992 --> 00:04:55,432
we'll give a satisfactory answer soon.

93
00:05:01,752 --> 00:05:02,552
We?

94
00:05:03,591 --> 00:05:05,175
Do you mean

95
00:05:05,351 --> 00:05:06,591
you and me?

96
00:05:08,552 --> 00:05:09,351
Yes.

97
00:05:10,632 --> 00:05:12,090
If you can't hold the line this time,

98
00:05:13,231 --> 00:05:14,391
I'll stand with you.

99
00:05:17,351 --> 00:05:18,151
Alright.

100
00:05:18,552 --> 00:05:19,791
No matter the reason,

101
00:05:20,710 --> 00:05:22,552
as long as you're willing
to stand by my side,

102
00:05:26,092 --> 00:05:27,292
that's enough.

103
00:05:39,391 --> 00:05:41,512
Zeyang.

104
00:05:42,432 --> 00:05:43,791
Boss Zhou.

105
00:05:44,391 --> 00:05:45,711
What a marvelous performance.

106
00:05:46,231 --> 00:05:47,911
Ha ha ha.

107
00:05:47,911 --> 00:05:49,271
This is all I have.

108
00:05:49,271 --> 00:05:50,791
I'll give it all to you.

109
00:05:51,791 --> 00:05:53,072
Please let Jiamin go.

110
00:05:53,312 --> 00:05:54,112
I'm begging you.

111
00:05:54,512 --> 00:05:55,552
Zeyang.

112
00:05:55,552 --> 00:05:56,872
Get up.

113
00:05:57,231 --> 00:05:58,432
I'm begging you.

114
00:05:58,952 --> 00:05:59,911
Please let Jiamin go.

115
00:06:02,831 --> 00:06:04,112
I'm begging you.

116
00:06:04,192 --> 00:06:04,831
Please.

117
00:06:05,911 --> 00:06:07,512
Ha ha ha.

118
00:06:08,391 --> 00:06:08,872
Well, well.

119
00:06:09,231 --> 00:06:11,992
I've got to admire
that little brain of yours.

120
00:06:12,231 --> 00:06:14,151
How did you come up

121
00:06:14,391 --> 00:06:17,512
with a thorough plan
in such a short time?

122
00:06:18,992 --> 00:06:22,552
Your petty scheme is scary.

123
00:06:22,791 --> 00:06:24,351
Ha ha ha.

124
00:06:26,791 --> 00:06:29,952
I told you, Qin Mo may talk tough,

125
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,752
but there's no way he doesn't care
about Qin Jiamin.

126
00:06:33,512 --> 00:06:35,391
As long as we have her,

127
00:06:35,911 --> 00:06:37,391
we have Qin Mo.

128
00:06:42,711 --> 00:06:45,231
The cops are hunting me
everywhere right now.

129
00:06:46,112 --> 00:06:47,752
Only here with you

130
00:06:47,752 --> 00:06:49,312
can I enjoy a moment of peace.

131
00:06:50,112 --> 00:06:51,831
If you hadn't told me

132
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:54,395
that intercepting this batch of palm oil
could bring Qin Mo down,

133
00:06:54,575 --> 00:06:56,736
I'd already be on a plane abroad.

134
00:06:57,112 --> 00:06:58,231
Hawaii.

135
00:06:58,591 --> 00:06:59,762
Sunbathing!

136
00:07:01,391 --> 00:07:02,192
Long,

137
00:07:03,072 --> 00:07:04,231
don't worry

138
00:07:04,231 --> 00:07:05,471
too much.

139
00:07:05,952 --> 00:07:07,992
Even though this palm oil order

140
00:07:08,112 --> 00:07:09,872
costs us all our money,

141
00:07:10,312 --> 00:07:11,312
just trust me,

142
00:07:11,632 --> 00:07:13,672
once Qin Mo falls,

143
00:07:14,552 --> 00:07:16,911
the entire Haicheng food market

144
00:07:17,312 --> 00:07:18,752
will belong to us.

145
00:07:19,911 --> 00:07:21,271
To your determination.

146
00:07:21,432 --> 00:07:21,872
Cheers.

147
00:07:21,992 --> 00:07:22,672
Cheers.

148
00:07:26,512 --> 00:07:27,432
Zhou Zeyang!

149
00:07:29,872 --> 00:07:30,391
Hey.

150
00:07:30,391 --> 00:07:31,231
Jiamin's here.

151
00:07:31,552 --> 00:07:32,552
Hide.

152
00:07:35,711 --> 00:07:36,737
Why are you here, Jiamin?

153
00:07:38,672 --> 00:07:40,362
Was it you behind the palm oil thing?

154
00:07:41,672 --> 00:07:42,687
You suspect me?

155
00:07:43,872 --> 00:07:45,351
Shouldn't I?

156
00:07:45,752 --> 00:07:47,552
Didn't we agree we only deal
with Zhuang Yan?

157
00:07:47,912 --> 00:07:48,952
What you're doing now

158
00:07:48,952 --> 00:07:50,962
will cut off
all of Jinxin's production lines

159
00:07:50,962 --> 00:07:52,763
and push the company
into a shutdown crisis.

160
00:07:52,887 --> 00:07:54,072
What is Qin Mo supposed to do?

161
00:07:56,151 --> 00:07:56,872
Baby,

162
00:07:57,231 --> 00:07:58,275
calm down.

163
00:07:58,992 --> 00:07:59,831
Sit.

164
00:08:01,775 --> 00:08:03,615
This really wasn't me.

165
00:08:04,072 --> 00:08:05,872
My company is so small.

166
00:08:05,911 --> 00:08:08,312
How could we buy an order that big?

167
00:08:08,487 --> 00:08:10,807
Think carefully, Jiamin.

168
00:08:10,875 --> 00:08:15,137
Who's been driving a wedge
between us all along?

169
00:08:16,591 --> 00:08:17,432
Zhuang Yan?

170
00:08:17,575 --> 00:08:18,415
Impossible.

171
00:08:18,512 --> 00:08:20,033
She's on my brother's side.

172
00:08:20,112 --> 00:08:21,980
What good would it do her
to bring down Jinxin?

173
00:08:23,391 --> 00:08:24,072
Jiamin,

174
00:08:25,231 --> 00:08:26,432
there's something

175
00:08:27,072 --> 00:08:29,072
I've been hesitating to tell you.

176
00:08:29,831 --> 00:08:32,152
You should know now.

177
00:08:33,312 --> 00:08:34,152
Zhuang Yan!

178
00:08:35,711 --> 00:08:38,231
You staged the whole palm oil incident
yourself, didn't you?

179
00:08:38,871 --> 00:08:40,600
Have you lost your mind, Qin Jiamin?

180
00:08:40,912 --> 00:08:43,072
Which eye of yours
saw me stage everything?

181
00:08:43,072 --> 00:08:44,111
Still denying it?

182
00:08:44,111 --> 00:08:45,111
You scheming liar!

183
00:08:46,511 --> 00:08:47,940
Do you dare admit who you really are?

184
00:08:47,952 --> 00:08:49,511
You are not Zhuang Yan!

185
00:08:49,511 --> 00:08:50,562
You impostor!

186
00:08:50,711 --> 00:08:51,032
Mo...

187
00:08:51,152 --> 00:08:51,952
Qin Jiamin,

188
00:08:52,890 --> 00:08:54,351
instead of looking for raw materials,

189
00:08:54,351 --> 00:08:55,690
what are you doing here causing a scene?

190
00:08:55,871 --> 00:08:56,650
Mo,

191
00:08:56,751 --> 00:08:58,552
didn't you hear me?

192
00:08:58,552 --> 00:08:59,912
She is not Zhuang Yan.

193
00:08:59,912 --> 00:09:00,991
Her background is unclear.

194
00:09:00,991 --> 00:09:01,991
Whether she is or not,

195
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,792
what does that have to do
with the palm oil?

196
00:09:21,952 --> 00:09:23,952
So you all knew her identity already?

197
00:09:24,192 --> 00:09:25,751
I was the only one kept in the dark?

198
00:09:26,231 --> 00:09:27,751
Jiamin, that's a separate issue.

199
00:09:28,190 --> 00:09:29,672
Right now, the most important thing

200
00:09:29,672 --> 00:09:31,192
is solving the palm oil problem.

201
00:09:31,192 --> 00:09:33,631
We should work together
to get through this,

202
00:09:33,631 --> 00:09:35,432
not create more trouble.

203
00:09:36,072 --> 00:09:36,631
Fine.

204
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:38,270
You all work together.

205
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,430
I'm the outsider here.

206
00:09:39,430 --> 00:09:40,711
I'll leave, okay?

207
00:09:48,711 --> 00:09:49,312
You...

208
00:09:51,231 --> 00:09:51,991
Don't worry.

209
00:09:53,511 --> 00:09:54,272
Let's continue.

210
00:09:55,351 --> 00:09:55,871
Come.

211
00:09:56,751 --> 00:09:58,231
We were talking about the palm oil.

212
00:10:04,272 --> 00:10:05,991
Why are you leaving again?

213
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:08,792
I can't stay in the same room
with someone of an unknown background.

214
00:10:08,792 --> 00:10:09,940
If she doesn't leave, I will.

215
00:10:09,950 --> 00:10:12,048
If you want to leave, fine.
Sign this first.

216
00:10:12,591 --> 00:10:15,152
This is a share transfer agreement

217
00:10:15,152 --> 00:10:16,952
approved by the company's shareholders.

218
00:10:17,631 --> 00:10:20,511
The price I'm offering is more than
Zhang Guolong could ever give you.

219
00:10:20,912 --> 00:10:22,072
If you really want to leave,

220
00:10:24,631 --> 00:10:25,392
sign it.

221
00:10:25,912 --> 00:10:27,471
Otherwise, once Jinxin halts production,

222
00:10:27,792 --> 00:10:30,471
your ten percent stake
won't be worth a thing.

223
00:10:30,812 --> 00:10:32,111
What do you mean?

224
00:10:32,625 --> 00:10:33,392
I know

225
00:10:34,032 --> 00:10:35,072
your apology was fake.

226
00:10:35,072 --> 00:10:36,880
What you really wanted
was to come back to Jinxin.

227
00:10:36,912 --> 00:10:37,831
I also know

228
00:10:38,991 --> 00:10:41,751
this incident has something
to do with Zhou Zeyang.

229
00:10:43,072 --> 00:10:43,871
Jiamin,

230
00:10:44,552 --> 00:10:45,831
you're my sister.

231
00:10:46,072 --> 00:10:47,192
No matter what you do to me,

232
00:10:47,192 --> 00:10:49,192
I can forgive you again and again.

233
00:10:49,675 --> 00:10:51,192
But as a shareholder,

234
00:10:51,991 --> 00:10:54,471
I can't watch you
keep harming the company.

235
00:10:57,552 --> 00:10:58,312
Sell your shares.

236
00:10:58,880 --> 00:10:59,952
Take the money and go back.

237
00:11:17,387 --> 00:11:18,600
(Share Transfer Agreement)

238
00:11:20,871 --> 00:11:22,312
You've grown up now.

239
00:11:24,192 --> 00:11:26,392
This is the freedom you always wanted.

240
00:11:27,831 --> 00:11:29,392
I hope you won't regret it.

241
00:11:44,591 --> 00:11:45,831
Qin Mo.

242
00:11:47,862 --> 00:11:50,381
I finally get to make you taste

243
00:11:50,962 --> 00:11:53,137
what it's like to be cornered.

244
00:11:54,412 --> 00:11:55,733
Zeyang.

245
00:11:57,187 --> 00:11:57,987
Jiamin?

246
00:11:59,032 --> 00:11:59,672
What's wrong?

247
00:11:59,672 --> 00:12:01,575
My brother doesn't want me anymore.

248
00:12:02,711 --> 00:12:03,792
There, there.

249
00:12:04,962 --> 00:12:06,083
It's okay.

250
00:12:06,392 --> 00:12:08,831
Qin Mo must've spoken in anger.

251
00:12:09,087 --> 00:12:10,991
He must be anxious,

252
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,860
given that something this big
is happening to Jinxin.

253
00:12:12,871 --> 00:12:14,511
What does he have to be anxious about?

254
00:12:14,672 --> 00:12:16,925
He's found a new supplier in Malaysia.

255
00:12:17,111 --> 00:12:19,152
Zhuang Yan has flown over
to sign the contract.

256
00:12:19,392 --> 00:12:21,072
I even handled
the purchase order myself.

257
00:12:21,631 --> 00:12:22,272
What?

258
00:12:22,792 --> 00:12:23,711
How is that possible?

259
00:12:28,392 --> 00:12:29,392
Why not?

260
00:12:29,552 --> 00:12:31,392
Mo always has a backup plan.

261
00:12:31,392 --> 00:12:32,552
The Malaysian supplier

262
00:12:32,552 --> 00:12:34,272
may not be as big as the Indonesian one,

263
00:12:34,471 --> 00:12:36,192
but their equipment is more advanced.

264
00:12:36,250 --> 00:12:38,392
Zhuang Yan also found several
other factories to help.

265
00:12:38,631 --> 00:12:40,511
All the problems
have already been solved.

266
00:12:41,287 --> 00:12:42,246
It's over.

267
00:12:45,262 --> 00:12:46,583
It's all over.

268
00:12:50,591 --> 00:12:51,392
Jiamin.

269
00:12:54,325 --> 00:12:55,246
What again?

270
00:12:55,392 --> 00:12:56,312
Nothing.

271
00:12:56,912 --> 00:12:57,912
I just want to ask.

272
00:12:58,110 --> 00:12:59,192
Does the palm oil incident

273
00:12:59,192 --> 00:13:00,970
have anything to do
with you and Zhou Zeyang?

274
00:13:01,591 --> 00:13:03,392
Zhuang Shanshan, what's your problem?

275
00:13:03,392 --> 00:13:04,940
What rights do you have
to accuse us like that?

276
00:13:04,952 --> 00:13:06,631
I know you won't believe me.

277
00:13:06,672 --> 00:13:08,180
You only trust Zhou Zeyang right now.

278
00:13:08,392 --> 00:13:09,751
I used to be like you.

279
00:13:09,751 --> 00:13:11,790
I was fooled by his sweet talk
for a long time too,

280
00:13:12,192 --> 00:13:13,687
until I discovered the truth myself.

281
00:13:14,312 --> 00:13:15,392
What truth?

282
00:13:16,072 --> 00:13:18,392
As for what it is,
you need to verify on your own.

283
00:13:18,991 --> 00:13:21,552
Don't you really want to know
what kind of person he is?

284
00:13:33,987 --> 00:13:36,550
(Palm Oil Purchase Order)

285
00:13:37,192 --> 00:13:38,672
(Now I know.)

286
00:14:03,925 --> 00:14:07,287
♪Flipping to a photo from that year♪

287
00:14:07,375 --> 00:14:10,525
♪Faded smiles burning bright♪

288
00:14:10,862 --> 00:14:14,075
♪I run back along the dates♪

289
00:14:14,225 --> 00:14:17,762
♪Searching in the cracks of time♪

290
00:14:18,025 --> 00:14:21,862
♪If I could relive that one second♪

291
00:14:22,087 --> 00:14:25,275
♪Open an umbrella early
at the street corner♪

292
00:14:25,537 --> 00:14:28,212
♪So you won't get wet
when you turn around♪

293
00:14:28,250 --> 00:14:32,925
♪Dodging that icy storm♪

294
00:14:34,462 --> 00:14:37,550
♪Let the hourglass flow backward♪

295
00:14:37,675 --> 00:14:41,225
♪I travel against time♪

296
00:14:41,850 --> 00:14:47,675
♪All regrets deserve to be remeasured♪

297
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:51,737
♪On the platform where we reunite♪

298
00:14:51,762 --> 00:14:56,287
♪I keep practicing my smile♪

299
00:14:57,392 --> 00:14:58,631
All these years,

300
00:14:59,991 --> 00:15:01,351
you must've been very tired.

301
00:15:24,075 --> 00:15:30,437
♪We stood side by side,
with no promises of forever♪

302
00:15:30,725 --> 00:15:37,612
♪We didn't know
that moment was already eternal♪

303
00:15:39,525 --> 00:15:44,637
♪The counter-clockwise hand
is ultimately nailed to eternity♪

304
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:12,538
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

305
00:16:12,663 --> 00:16:15,975
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

306
00:16:16,138 --> 00:16:19,725
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

307
00:16:20,025 --> 00:16:23,313
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

308
00:16:23,538 --> 00:16:27,163
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

309
00:16:27,325 --> 00:16:30,663
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

310
00:16:30,738 --> 00:16:34,450
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

311
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:38,363
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

312
00:16:38,425 --> 00:16:44,475
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

313
00:16:45,650 --> 00:16:52,388
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

314
00:16:52,675 --> 00:16:56,950
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

315
00:16:56,950 --> 00:17:00,250
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

316
00:17:00,325 --> 00:17:04,625
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

317
00:17:04,688 --> 00:17:08,338
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

318
00:17:08,338 --> 00:17:11,900
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

319
00:17:11,950 --> 00:17:15,213
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

320
00:17:15,213 --> 00:17:18,963
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

321
00:17:18,963 --> 00:17:25,675
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
